<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>GAME_PAGE</title>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
  <h1>King's Cup: <small>drinking with friends!</small></h1>
</nav>
    
</head>
</header>
<main>

  <section id="gameboard">
    <div class="row">
      <div id="top_row">
        <ul>

          <% if current_game.players.size >= 1 %>
          <li>
            <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
          <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100" alt="Responsive image" id="avatar" /> 
        </div>
          </li>
          <% end %>

           <% if current_game.players.size >= 3 %>
          <li>
            <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
          <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100" alt="Responsive image"/>
        </div>
          </li>
          <% end %>

          <% if current_game.players.size >= 5 %>
          <li>
            <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
          <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100" alt="Responsive image" />
        </div>
          </li>
          <% end %>

          <% if current_game.players.size >= 7 %>
          <li>
            <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
          <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100" alt="Responsive image" />
        </div>
          </li>
          <% end %>

        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div id="middle-row">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <div class="col-md-3 card">
            <form action="/turn" method="post"> 
              <input type="hidden" name="current_player" value="<%= @current_player %>"></input>

              <button class="card_picker">
                <img class="card1" src="/images/cardback.jpg" alt="Responsive image" style="width:100px" />
              </button>
            </form>
      </div>
        </li>
        <% if @turn.card %>
        <li>
          <div class="col-md-3 card">
            <img class="card1" src="/<%= @turn.card.url %>" style="width:95px"></img>
            <%= current_game.current_player %>
            <%= @turn.id %>
      </div>
        </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
    <div id="small-img">
      <ul>

      <% if current_game.players.size >= 2 %>
        <li>
          <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
            <p>name</p>
        <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100" alt="Responsive image" /> 
      </div>
        </li>
        <% end %>

        <% if current_game.players.size >= 4 %>
        <li>
          <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
            <p>name</p>
        <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100"  alt="Responsive image"/>
      </div>
        </li>
        <% end %>

        <% if current_game.players.size >= 6 %>
        <li>
          <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
            <p>name</p>
        <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100" alt="Responsive image" />
      </div>
        </li>
        <% end %>

        <% if current_game.players.size == 8 %>
        <li>
          <div class="col-md-3 avatar">
            <p>name</p>
        <img src="http://placehold.it/150x100"  alt="Responsive image"  />
      </div>
        </li>
        <% end %>

      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>


  <aside id="sidebar">
    <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
  <li role="presentation"><a href="#" onclick="toggle_visibility('foo');">RULES:</a>
<div id="foo" style="display: none">
<h4>Ace: Snake-Eyes</h4>
 Call anyone snake eyes in the game. No one can look at the person with snake eyes until another ace is picked or they have a drink.
<br>
<h4>2: YOU</h4> 
 Drawing player picks a person from the circle who has to sip 
<br>
<h4>3: ME</h4>
Drawing player has to sip!
<br>
<h4>4: Whores</h4>
 All girls have a sip
<br>
<h4>5: Bust-A-Jive</h4>
Pick a dance move. The next person has to do that dance move and add to it. This continues until someone screws up and must sip  
<br>
<h4>6: Dicks</h4>
All the guys have a sip 
<br>
<h4>7: Seven-Heaven</h4>
 All players point a finger to the sky.Last player to do must sip
<br>
<h4>8: Mate</h4>
Whenever you drink they must sip 
<br>
<h4>9: Nine-Rhyme</h4>
Pick a word. Go around the circle with each person rhyming. First person to repeat a word or not have a word must sip. 
<br>
<h4>10: Categories</h4>
Pick a category.Go around the circle naming things in that category.First person to repeat or not answer must sip
<br>
<h4>Jack: Never-Have-I-Ever</h4>
 everybody puts up 3 to 5 fingers and drawing player says something they haven't done before and then go around the circle. The first person with all their fingers down must sip 
<br>
<h4>Queen: Question-Master</h4>
Whenever you ask a question to someone they must answer with a question or they sip 
<br>
<h4>Kings Cup!</h4>
Make a rule and whenever someone breaks that rule from now on they must sip.
</div>
</ul>
